Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:18.52,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Proud of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.77,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Manners? I left them behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:24.27,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Hold up hold up 抑えようなんて無駄 Duh duh
