Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:30.74,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Boy you’re playing with fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:32.36,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}負ける気しないわ
