Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.39,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}とめられない You can’t kill my vibe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.69,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}自由に I can blow your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.69,0:02:04.52,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}何度だって You’ll see me rise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:05.98,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Tryna get to me and pay the price
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.03,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}描いた未来へ　進んで行くだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.82,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Won’t look back
