Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.34,0:01:12.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}走自己的路 莫要阻拦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.05,0:01:14.64,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}迈向巅峰
